ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="9c44468e-cd5e-43eb-8859-437974ea04ae" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Graph First Feeding Time" Description="Graph of a Pen's feeding time" CreatedDT="2014-03-24T11:09:22.753" ModifiedDT="2015-03-26T10:30:45.443" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAdcyY=" ReportVersion="0" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select z.* from ( select p.PenNumber ,fs.InstanceDate as ReportDate ,dl.LocationName as PenName ,it.StartTime ,c.CompanyName ,ppt.PenTypeName as PrimaryPenType from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join Location dl on dl.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Pen p on p.LocationGID = dl.LocationGID join Company c on c.CompanyGID = dl.CompanyGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID cross apply (select CAST(CONVERT(TIME, MIN(DATEADD(second, -it.DurationSeconds, it.TransactionDT))) AS DATETIME) as 'StartTime' from InventoryTransaction it join Location l on l.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID where it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID and l.LocationType = 1 group by it.ToHistoryLocationGID) it cross apply (select top 1 pt.PenTypeName from PenPenType ppt join PenType pt on pt.PenTypeGID = ppt.PenTypeGID where ppt.PenGID = p.PenGID and ppt.IsPrimary = 1 and ppt.Inactive = 0) ppt ) z where (1 = 1)</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
